{"tid":1122721,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"夫訂閱色情電視頻道　老婦大怒轟斃枕邊人","createTime":"2019-04-24T05:46:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-24T09:27:55.000Z","uid":22675,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e39c14a2aec44ff8a8fa86f1c41c867fa0592a4b","tid":1122721,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T05:46:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20190424/photo/bkn-20190424070009537-0424_00972_001_01p.jpg?20190424071110\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Famenews%2F20190424%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190424070009537-0424_00972_001_01p.jpg%3F20190424071110&h=bdc29bb2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國阿肯色州一名老婦去年疑因發現丈夫訂閱色情電視頻道，憤然替對方取消訂單。詎料她其後依然收到帳單，才得悉丈夫繼續偷偷私下訂閱，一怒之下竟舉槍轟斃枕邊人。被控謀殺的她周一（22日）出庭時辯稱自己無罪，並形容丈夫訂閱色情資料是侮辱她的行為。 <br />\n<br />\n69歲的被告帕特里夏（Patricia Hill）被控於去年7月，在位於小石城（Little Rock）附近的家中，與65歲丈夫希爾（Frank Hill）因訂閱色情電視頻道的問題發生爭執。她涉嫌向希爾開了兩槍將他擊斃。 <br />\n<br />\n帕特里夏的代表律師表示，其當事人認為希爾訂閱色情電視頻道，是侮辱她以及她的宗教。案件仍在審理當中，醫生將會評估帕特里夏的精神狀態。"},{"pid":"9f62c8a851ff92e7e9b0158d380dc6789a3f2766","tid":1122721,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T05:53:18.000Z","msg":"女性或宗教正義支持者，或會支持老婦(雖然行為已喪失另一人牲命)？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e1b08cb21e0a672696340010fa1a579b1a8d8b8","tid":1122721,"uid":4826,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T05:55:59.000Z","msg":"呢單新聞應該比所有女權撚睇完之後效法"},{"pid":"e74d2436ec4c71a942da602fdf5a9a64537a651c","tid":1122721,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T05:56:12.000Z","msg":"小石城?<br />\npokemon?"},{"pid":"604beec27da47432952d05fab1583f6a238b5666","tid":1122721,"uid":158411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T05:57:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6d384588b81428b59524e7b5cff3287e11805cc","tid":1122721,"uid":197920,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"0e1b08cb21e0a672696340010fa1a579b1a8d8b8","tid":1122721,"uid":4826,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T05:55:59.000Z","msg":"呢單新聞應該比所有女權撚睇完之後效法"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T05:57:38.000Z","msg":"又關女權咩事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n件事同性別平等有咩關係"},{"pid":"e28d1028db9fc3b46f1028dfdb5c01bfecd393df","tid":1122721,"uid":175661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T06:15:00.000Z","msg":"睇吓鹹片都唔撚得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65725b2e5f754e4a216926ceb27dce488309e421","tid":1122721,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T09:27:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}